@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy"; // Sets the title of the page
}

<style>
    h1 {
        color: #007bff; /* Blue color for headings */
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add some space below the heading */
    }

    p {
        color: #6c757d; /* Gray color for paragraphs */
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add some space below the paragraph */
        font-size: 16px; /* Adjust font size for better readability */
    }

    .privacy-image {
        max-width: 100%; /* Ensure the image fits within its container */
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add some space below the image */
    }
</style>

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1> <!-- Displays the title of the page -->

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1584433144859-1fc3ab64a957?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Nnx8cHJpdmFjeXxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D" alt="Privacy Policy" class="privacy-image"> <!-- Displays an image related to privacy policy -->

<p>Your privacy is important to us. It is our policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you.</p> <!-- Privacy policy statement -->

<p>We only ask for personal information when we truly need it to provide a service to you. We collect it by fair and lawful means, with your knowledge and consent.</p> <!-- Information collection statement -->

<p>We only retain collected information for as long as necessary to provide you with your requested service, and we protect it within commercially acceptable means to prevent loss, theft, or unauthorized access.</p> <!-- Information retention and protection statement -->

<p>We do not share any personally identifying information publicly or with third-parties, except when required to by law.</p> <!-- Information sharing statement -->

<p>Your continued use of our website will be regarded as acceptance of our practices around privacy and personal information.</p> <!-- Acceptance statement -->

<p>If you have any questions about how we handle user data and personal information, feel free to contact us.</p> <!-- Contact information statement -->
